description:

Step into Setera — where space, time, and sanity come undone.

Chrono Odyssey is an open-world action MMORPG that casts players into the world of Setera, a mysterious land scarred by war and shrouded in cosmic horror. Wield the power to manipulate space and time as you face nightmarish entities beyond human comprehension. Forge your path through ever-shifting realities, where combat meets madness.

Master time. Brave the unknown. Reclaim a ruined world from cosmic doom.
